data.description: Bright Four-Bedroom Family Home in East Cobb!    Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after East Cobb area. This large two-story traditional house offers everything a family could desire, from spacious bedrooms to modern amenities and a fantastic location within walking distance to Walton High School and Dodgen Middle School.  HUGE MEDIA ROOM: Enjoy quality family time in the expansive media room, complete with a mini-split HVAC system installed in 2019 for year-round comfort.  SPACIOUS PRIMARY SUITE: Relax in your primary suite with a sitting area and vaulted ceilings, providing a private retreat within your own home.  FAMILY FRIENDLY NEIGHBORHOOD: Located on a corner lot in a family-friendly area, this home is perfect for kids and parents alike. Ideal for walking and biking.  MASSIVE BACKYARD: Vast and flat fenced backyard offers privacy and space for outdoor activities, gardening, and entertaining.  Great place for the dogs!  NEW SHED: A very large 10'x16' custom built shed, matching the house's aesthetics, provides ample storage space for all your needs.  RECENT UPDATES: This home has seen significant renovations in 2019, including replacement of both furnaces and AC units, new windows, house wrap, Hardie-Plank siding, roof, water heater, front and back doors, and a mini-split HVAC system in the upstairs media room.  REPLUMBED WITH PEX: Worried about East Cobb copper pipe pin-hole leaks? You should be! Rest easy knowing this house was fully replumbed with PEX in 2022, ensuring a reliable and efficient plumbing system.  CONSISTENT COMFORT: Open cell spray foam attic insulation installed in 2023 and new air ducts in 2021 guarantee consistent and comfortable temperatures on the second floor.  CONVENIENT LOCATION: Walton High School and Dodgen Middle School are within walking distance, and you'll find shopping, dining, and parks nearby for your convenience. NO HOA.     This East Cobb gem is move-in ready and offers a perfect blend of modern updates and timeless charm. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home!    Property has an assumable 3.0% FHA mortgage with a balance of $279,000.
